  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc8 \u0b86\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0baf\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b85\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Important Notice of the Commissioner General of Examinations",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It has been announced that the 2022 Class 5 Scholarship Examination and General Certificate of Education Higher Level Examinations will begin in the coming month of December.",
        "It has been informed that the Grade 5 Scholarship Examination will begin on the 4th of December.",
        "Meanwhile, the Commissioner of Examinations has said that the high-level examinations, which will begin on December 5, will be held from the first week of January 2023. (R)"
